{"type": "article", "id": 27723, "title": "像阳台栏杆的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-03T06:59:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021200562aOVwH3zPK8kbr5E.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>薄荷绿的坐垫搭配木质的沙发架，<a href=\"http://www.dam.pt\">DAM</a> 设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.dam.pt/products/?id=39\">Valentim</a> 的沙发带给人一种清爽的美感，是一个很适合夏天的设计。它的造型灵感来源于阳台的围栏，扶手的靠垫弧度与圆柱形状的胡桃木非常贴合，看起来就像是慵懒地搭在上面一样。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120055d5rO2y3XT7CL1VZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120055uXnrVmfgWhMobSAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120055kQ1U3CYyvuSdthpa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120056HfpEwro0P3TSDI2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}